<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-5968] Remove all broker metrics during shutdown</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-5968</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;RequestMetrics on the broker is currently a static variable, created when the broker starts up, but the metrics are never removed. This makes it hard to test broker metrics since there could be metrics left over from previous tests. We should ensure that all metrics are cleared even for brokers.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13104690">KAFKA-5968</key>
            <summary>Remove all broker metrics during shutdown</summary>
